\id 1TI - Sembeleke (SGI1TI.01) Samberigi PNG 1Timothy 01 13/2/91 Macnaughtan
\h 1 TIMODI
\toc1 Polomaęž‰ Timodi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke titinaęž‰ wapee
\toc2 1 Timodi
\toc3 1 Timodi
\mt1 Polomaęž‰ Timodi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke titinaęž‰ wapee
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Polo IĚ±taęž‰ mo Ketiso Yesunaęž‰ aposolo hali halome. Nikaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make mo epenaęž‰ yu wia halomaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu yaapomaęž‰ do e pokono lelepeme.
\p 
\v 2 Do wape Timodi neke paęž‰taęž‰ wape pitolome. Mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ ya weki haleme. Mo Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu nikaęž‰ Tekehali ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make puki lopaasaęž‰eki make neke paęž‰taęž‰ kinaęž‰e.
\s1 Makeaasaęž‰ hau walaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu
\p 
\v 3 IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande Maęž‰sedonia nane pulu hataęž‰ loaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ame make neketaęž‰ mo Epesese nane pa hao hapeke alome. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ haleme mandane haliwekimaęž‰ iki makeaasaęž‰ haumanu walo halemeeki na walepepee loelenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.
\v 4 Mo haliweki ikaęž‰ napeke na pitiki pimanu make ikaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ bikimanu yataęž‰po hataęž‰ alemeeki make paeyao minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰ lapeke. Kutu piki pi lo haleme ekimaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeaalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu minaęž‰ na tambaęž‰ mikitaęž‰ ape ape laęž‰ tiaalieke. Mo epeaalo paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone tulaalomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ homeke miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 5 Mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ na lapepee lapeke alo ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hone teke yako pea make ikaęž‰ puki lopao make ikaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulao halimi ekimaęž‰ make koto haumanu pilimi ekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pea haenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.
\v 6 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ do haumanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo hande popeke na piki pimanu hotu haleme ekimaęž‰ epeke hau peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰manu handaęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ hali haluekee hone wia hataęž‰ dupaęž‰paęž‰peke dupaęž‰paęž‰peke pimanu wopu alemepate pa mo ikaęž‰ aleme pi kone hone wopu na u make koto pinaęž‰ teke make hone wopu na witelememe.
\v 8 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Lo Pi manumaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ homeke pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke hone witolomaęž‰pate
\v 9 pa dupiki hone make witolomaęž‰me. Mo lo pi manutaęž‰ mo epeke wandaęž‰hali tikitiki yaaluekemaęž‰ na ulaęž‰pate pa mo ikaęž‰ you hali paęž‰taęž‰ homu na piki pa pi yambolo haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Dupae. Kodaęž‰ hoki walaa hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki kenke alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone u haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make inkiki ateke kone lu make mandane wandaęž‰hali lu homao haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make kutupa mo
\v 10 yolaęž‰laęž‰ hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ pa hali yankeke paęž‰taęž‰ kone pitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mandane wandaęž‰hali pake minaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make yayapiki pi lo haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make ya pi alo kone Tekehalinaęž‰ biki lo haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make kutu piki hau piteleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ koto lo pimanu wia paęž‰laęž‰me. Do lo pimanu ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo epeke tikitiki piki manaęž‰ pimanu aęž‰mbaasaęž‰ hoke haumanu saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ ulaęž‰me.
\v 11 Koto walaęž‰peke manaęž‰ pi epeketaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ piki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ la halonoyeke kaęž‰laęž‰ Pi Seliapo paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me.
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ keiyae leekeeki
\p 
\v 12 Ya e pokono wele peaasaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu nikaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alome. Ipikaęž‰ e IĚ±maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ pokaalieke hone wia IĚ± maĚ±leke lieke ekinaęž‰ keiyae alome.
\v 13 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ biki hoke pi pi alo hataęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiao make iki tekipuleke laasaęž‰ hali haowaęž‰me. Kutu puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulao make mo puaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ hone wopu na wiki hataęž‰ pueke handaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 14 Nikaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ wopu kuaęž‰niaeyekeme. Kutupa make mo nikaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± molome hone tulaasaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make kiaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 15 Otaęž‰ opua hone tulaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa. Ketiso Yesumaęž‰ hoke hau pu halomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali daęž‰taaluekemaęž‰ yeke do kenkenaęž‰ epeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hoke hau wopu pitaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ IĚ± yaęž‰pate
\v 16 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Ketiso Yesumaęž‰ mo wetepe hone tulao daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki mulu peleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pieketaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make pinaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la walaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 17 Mo lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yo make homaęž‰peke na yo piki daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰ Kini hali ipiki homeke kone Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ biki tieke otaęž‰ kende winaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyaenaęž‰ laęž‰naęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.
\p 
\v 18 Ya weki Timodio. IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ neke hone witolo hataęž‰ laęž‰ wiaęž‰ pitaęž‰ koto laęž‰ wiaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone ame nakanaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰peke alome. Koto laęž‰ wiaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ale leke miniki hataęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ peaęž‰peke.
\v 19 Kutupa nakaęž‰ hone tulaleeki wopu miniki hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone tekemanu haĚ±iĚ± peaapaęž‰naęž‰ wopu handeteke hapeke. Mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tekemanu pendulu baemeke handaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekitaęž‰ mo hande sisima kawasotaęž‰ toopinaęž‰ tulaaso yambolo hoetaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaasemeeki make koto tupaęž‰ kone otaęž‰ hoeyaasememe.
\v 20 Mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± haepeke hali yaapo ipilikaęž‰ biki Haimeniasi pitaęž‰ Aęž‰lekesaęž‰nda yaapotaęž‰ koto hau pipikime. Ipiliki tanda minaęž‰ mo Sadaninaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰naęž‰ tapaowaęž‰me. Kutu pu ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki laasepeeki minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰ tambaęž‰ milieke.
\c 2
\s1 Siosi tapakenaęž‰ mombela yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 1-2 Ya sutiaaso titinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ dupa. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao make ikaęž‰ kini haliweki make kapomani e pokaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ honke lo hapaęž‰peke. Kutaa make ikinaęž‰ keiyae lo hapaęž‰peke. Koto yeni pulu peleme ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰ alome. Iki niki paeyao yopu hao polumanaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tikitiki piki hau mumanaęž‰ alome.
\v 3 Kutu piki yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo niki paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰me.
\v 4 Ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki mea hataęž‰ mo otaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teke handaęž‰ winaęž‰e.
\v 5 Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ homeke halaęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali nikaęž‰ kaęž‰pa hali homeketaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu halaęž‰me.
\v 6 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰ wieke nate opolo epeeketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paa hambuluekemaęž‰ ipiki kone haleekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ walolotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰e laa hone paęž‰laęž‰eki peneme yaalaęž‰me.
\v 7 Koto pi walono yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± aposolo hano laęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ yaa pi na alome. Otaęž‰ pi alo loaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ tiaasaęž‰ hali hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi make mo hone tulaasaęž‰eki make walaano yeke hano laęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 8 IĚ±maęž‰ Siosi paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ halimaęž‰ yeni pinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Hali epimaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankolo o kake neli pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau na piki otaęž‰ yako piki hone u paleke halaęž‰ hali manumaęž‰ mo siosinaęž‰ mombilimi paęž‰taęž‰ kiki aęž‰meiyao yeni pinaęž‰e.
\s1 Wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ peaęž‰peke haumanu
\p 
\v 9 Wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ make dupiki pi alome. Ikaęž‰ dau manutaęž‰ epekeeki ikaęž‰ anaęž‰ piki tupaęž‰ kone yamaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kimelemaęž‰ hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ itiki loke yaaponaęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ make o beleke manumaęž‰ make o yenki tieke yeke akaęž‰manu au na lapaęž‰peke.
\v 10 Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandiki haluekemaęž‰ hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke haumanu pu hapaęž‰peke. Kutu piteleme hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ ikaęž‰ au seliapoe.
\v 11 Wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone minaęž‰niao yopu siki pitaęž‰ mo pimanu opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ you wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰e hone na witolome. Diaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ pi na leke pitaęž‰ opitaęž‰laęž‰eki homeke piaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa laęž‰ witolome.
\v 13 Do ekinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰la wepiaataęž‰ Ipaęž‰taęž‰ wetepe wepiekeme.
\v 14 Kutupa Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo Sadanimaęž‰ makeaeyeke pi na opiekepate ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Ipimaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi yambeleekeme.
\v 15 Kutu piekepate wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ weki taapolo hataęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ kimelemaęž‰ hone tulao pukimaęž‰ homaa tikitiki piki hone taapunaęž‰ hataęž‰ pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ weki mendilimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki saęž‰saęž‰ pilieke.
\c 3
\s1 Siosi tapake handeteke halaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Otaęž‰ pi alaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ doe. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰hali hatuku polueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epeke e hone koto witaęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e.
\v 2 Ketiso wandaęž‰hali hatuku pulaęž‰ halitaęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki hali yelieke. Ipikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ homeke maęž‰laęž‰ halie. Ipikitaęž‰ hone wotu lenkene pea ulaęž‰ halie. Ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ e na kapaęž‰lake epeke tupaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ halie. Mo na handeke wandaęž‰hali make ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mea peliaasaęž‰ hali yelieke. Ipikitaęž‰ pi epeke tupaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ halie.
\v 3 Hoke ikali naa lu keaasaęž‰ hali o tekipuleke laasaęž‰ hali diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate ipikitaęž‰ yopu hataęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± puluekemaęž‰ na taapaęž‰laęž‰ halie. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ mani paęž‰taęž‰ we na pambeke halaęž‰ halie.
\v 4 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ wopu handeteke hataęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone wia ipikaęž‰ pi opinaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 5 Mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ kone handeteke hapeke na yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ekipa handeteke hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 6 Handaenaęž‰ hau pea lopaamaęž‰naęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ pi panake minaęž‰laęž‰ hali na halieke. Mo hande Sadani lopeeke tupaęž‰ lopaamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 7 Ipikitaęž‰ mo Ketiso na haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ pi laalimikie. Kutu pilie ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki na hoeyaaso haenaęž‰ mo hande Sadanimaęž‰ honaęž‰maasaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ na lopilieke.
\s1 Siosi tapake tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki
\p 
\v 8 Kutupa dikoni haliweki make kekeke yaapo na haasaęž‰ hali make epeke hau pu haleme haliweki hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaa make ikitaęž‰ mo hande waini ikali wotu na no haleme haliweki make yenki hakaęž‰taęž‰pao muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu peleme haliweki hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 9 Kutupa hokeeki ikaęž‰ hone teke paęž‰taęž‰ na u pelia haenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo walaęž‰ tiaeyeke otaęž‰ pimanu wotu miniki hao halimikie.
\v 10 Koto haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu haleme haumanu handomaęž‰ tiatiki peaataęž‰ anaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo e pokaenaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 11 Koto haliwekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ make ikaęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone manumaęž‰ tekele tekele pea hataęž‰ pi la la na piki wandaęž‰weki halimikie. Epeke hone wia hoto paeyao ikaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰ pi yaapomaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau homeke pu hapeke yeke wandaęž‰weki halimikie.
\v 12 Dikoni halitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ homeke maęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ wopu handeteke hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ halie.
\v 13 Mo e epeke tupaęž‰ pokaaseme dikoni haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke halimi ekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰taęž‰ epeke biki wilie haliweki halimikie. Kutaa make ikaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke pi lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ teke pi
\p 
\v 14 Neke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do wape pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ neke aĚ±iĚ± koto kone handolo ipulueke hone wia halopate
\v 15 ale maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± saęž‰saęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ hataęž‰ pulu polomaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ do wapemaęž‰ walieke. Koto tapaketaęž‰ mo daęž‰taa hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi tapake loaęž‰me. Koto siositaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pitaęž‰ tia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pinki tieke leke halaęž‰me.
\v 16 Mo nikaęž‰ Ketiso haunaęž‰ teketaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau tieke diaęž‰me pitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Do ekinaęž‰ alome.
\q1 Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ halinaęž‰ loke kone mea opolo epeekeme.
\q1 Mo hande Sipitidimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yako paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekie laa peneme waleekeme.
\q1 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ make handeekeme.
\q1 Ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ mo tutu maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰manu make walemekeme.
\q1 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekeme.
\q1 Kutaa ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ oli ya nane hatuku mea peekeme.
\c 4
\s1 Mandane makeaasaęž‰ pimanu walaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali
\p 
\v 1 Mo Sipitidimaęž‰ peneme yao dupa alaęž‰me. Wetepe ninaęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hone tulaasaęž‰ hautaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalimikie laęž‰laęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo yayapiki pi aleme sipitidi manunaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homa hataęž‰ mo hoke temoko manunaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰eki telimikie.
\v 2 Koto walaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo makeaaso yayapiki pi lo haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ peo lalememe. Mo talo talo hake toopi wepikimaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ to tokulaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone teketaęž‰ to tokulaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 3 Kutu pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make mandane nemanu halaęž‰eki make hoke haue laa wahapaęž‰ peao halememe. Pate do ne manutaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nomono yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wepiayekeme laa ipikaęž‰ pi minaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ hau homeke hone witolo hataęž‰ koto ne manunaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alo hataęž‰ napeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 4 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wepieke alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ epeke ale manue. Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ wahapaęž‰ pu kiaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate paeyaotaęž‰ pa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alo hataęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 5 Pa ekipeke. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi pitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae laa yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapomaęž‰ mo ne paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na taĚ±leĚ±naęž‰ lelieke.
\s1 Ketiso Yesunaęž‰ epeke e pokaasaęž‰ hali
\p 
\v 6 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do manaęž‰ pimanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ mo Ketiso kametonu paęž‰taęž‰ la halo haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ Ketiso Yesunaęž‰ epeke e pokaasaęž‰ hali halipikie. Kotaęž‰ koto nakanaęž‰maęž‰ teliele hone tulaasaęž‰ pi pitaęž‰ mo waleaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu miniki hao haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutu pilipi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ neke wele pealieke.
\v 7 Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo epe na piki Kodaęž‰ mataake tindemanu mokaęž‰laa kitemeeki kiaapeke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ hande hande pu hapeke.
\v 8 Lokenaęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ hande hande pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ niki pa hosikimaęž‰ epeaaliepate pa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ hande hande pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ niki otaęž‰ epeaalieke. Pa ekipeke. Koto haumaęž‰taęž‰ ame do nikaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ halomaęž‰eki make wetepe daęž‰taa halo polomaęž‰eki make anaęž‰lawalieke.
\v 9 Otaęž‰ opua hone tulaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupae.
\v 10 Kodaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ hali halaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasomaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ hali halaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto daęž‰taa hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti lalomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ bepolaluekemaęž‰ honkopu hao e wopu poko halomaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 11 Do manaęž‰manu make do walaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opua otaęž‰ peaęž‰tiki pu haenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ wopu walo hapeke.
\v 12 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ neke wekihali hale ekinaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pa wekie laamaęž‰naęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketiso hau mokaęž‰laęž‰ tiaapeke. Koto puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pilipi haumaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ lelipi pimaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homilipi ekimaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ hone tulalipi ekimaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ tikitiki piki haumaęž‰ make koto hau paeyaotaęž‰ mo pi mineleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ otaęž‰ handenaęž‰ lapeke.
\v 13 IĚ± aęž‰pono moĚ±luĚ± hataęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ natemanu wiaataęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ opinaęž‰ mo Baibolo pimanu yataęž‰paęž‰laęž‰eki make mo pi walaęž‰laęž‰eki make walaęž‰ tiaaso la halaęž‰laęž‰eki make koto hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu hao putia puaęž‰peke.
\v 14 Mo siosi you haliwekimaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ younaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiki wimi dinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke kitaęž‰laęž‰ epeke ale homeke nakaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ wiayaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lapeke.
\v 15 Paeyaomaęž‰ nakaęž‰ Ketiso hau daeyaaso piteleeki handenaęž‰ do IĚ±maęž‰ la kitolo ekimanu nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wopu wia mokaęž‰laęž‰ hande hande pu hapeke.
\v 16 Nakaęž‰ walele ekimanu make nakaęž‰ pu hale hau make wopu handeteke hapeke. Do haumanu paeyao epeke tupaęž‰ putia pekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pilipi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ neke make mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ walele pi opua ipu haleme wandaęž‰hali make detelimikie.
\c 5
\s1 Siosi wandaęž‰hali handeteke hataęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Mo koke haliweki na tolu lu pelepatetaęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ale tupaęž‰ homu piki pimanu lapeke. Panake haliweki make nakaęž‰ kame tupaęž‰ kone epeaapeke.
\v 2 Koke wandaęž‰weki make nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone handeteke hataęž‰taęž‰ panake wandaęž‰weki make nakaęž‰ anaęž‰ leke tikitiki piki haumaęž‰ homeke handeteke hapeke.
\p 
\v 3 Kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honumake siki halaęž‰eki handekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone epeke u hapeke.
\v 4 Pate ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki o eiyeke wanekenaęž‰ wekiwandiki hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰la ikaęž‰ koke wandaęž‰ handeteke hasaęž‰ hau peaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu piki hau pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande ateke inkiki make aeyeke meiyekemaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pimi ekimanu hombo peaasememe. Koto haumaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰me.
\v 5 Kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki tambaęž‰ minaęž‰yeke ipikaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yalo ipikaęž‰ honumake siki hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki handeteke haenaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti lao halaęž‰me. Kutu pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki tambaęž‰ minaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ timbaęž‰ nate yaaponaęž‰ honke pa alo alo hataęž‰ yeni pu halaęž‰me.
\v 6 Pate kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ namonamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu homekenaęž‰ hone u hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pa halaęž‰pate kone ipikaęž‰ temokotaęž‰ homa ulaęž‰me.
\v 7 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoelaęž‰me laamaęž‰naęž‰ do manaęž‰ pimanu wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰la halaęž‰tiki pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 8 Kutu pilipipate maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapakemanu o otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ na handeteke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ mo Ketiso hau kiaaso toopi mea baasaęž‰me. Kutu piki somenaęž‰ hoke haumaęž‰taęž‰ mo pi na miki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau lombei pea otaęž‰ hoelaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 9 Mo kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰wekinaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ wapenaęž‰taęž‰ dupiki wandaęž‰naęž‰ biki homeke wiaęž‰peke. Wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bapi hali tieke tepo paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make ipikitaęž‰ hali homekenaęž‰ da peeke wandaęž‰ make
\v 10 wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ epeke hau piaęž‰ wandaęž‰e aleme wandaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hayaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make na handeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali epemeke handaęž‰mea wamo piaęž‰tiki pieke wandaęž‰ make Ketiso yankeketonu oto nane hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ mieke wandaęž‰ make kaęž‰ndaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali peteleaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make epeke haumanu puluekemaęž‰ hone wopu u hayeke wandaęž‰ make kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ koto hau paeyao tonkaęž‰naęž‰ apaęž‰tao peaęž‰tiki pieki handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki wape peaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 11 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate mandane moputali kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰manu ikaęž‰ bikimanu wape pea na apaęž‰taapeke. Pa ekipeke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone pelemeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ da puluekemaęž‰ Ketiso hoki walaa pelimikie.
\v 12 Kutu pimikinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la laęž‰ wimiki pimanu yambilimikie.
\v 13 Kutaa make kutupiki kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ da yalayala pu pominolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ e pokaęž‰peke natemanu hoeyaalememe. Koto hau homeke diaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kotoeki otaęž‰ lombeipiki hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa. Mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hau hotiataęž‰ laęž‰ mundula mundula pitolo hataęž‰ mo otaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu laęž‰ tiatia pu halememe.
\v 14 Mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ piteleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi loluekemaęž‰ waleke wiaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo Ketiso halaęž‰ moputali kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰wekitaęž‰ pa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ da pua wekiwandiki mendia ikaęž‰ da handeteke haenaęž‰e hone witolome.
\v 15 Pate mandane kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ manutaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la Sadani teli mea pelememe.
\v 16 Kutu pu halemepate Ketiso wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰manu maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Siosi tapake paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ wiaamaęž‰naęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo siosi tapakemaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo honumake siki haleme kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰weki otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ waleke wilieke.
\p 
\v 17 Ikaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali handeteke hataęž‰ e epeke tupaęž‰ pokemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ biki aęž‰meiyaaso yenki anaęž‰naęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao minaęž‰e hone wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo pi walaęž‰pekeeki o manaęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ tiaaso hataęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu hao wopu pokemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutu piki you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la hone wia peaęž‰peke.
\v 18 Do alo ekinaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kaomaęž‰ palaowa kilikimanu ambuku mea baaluekemaęž‰ ankemaęž‰ e pokolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake ankaęž‰taęž‰pu na peaęž‰peke lo make mo e pokaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ yenki miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa wape pea ulaęž‰me.
\v 19 Wandaęž‰hali homekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo you halimaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰piki hau piaęž‰me leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na opuaęž‰peke. Koto pilipipate hali yaapo tepomaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰pa leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ opuaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 20 You halimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ hoke hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mandane you haliwekimaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ hone winaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke potopoto kone ipikaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰eki laa la halaataęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ peaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 21 Mo Kodaęž‰ make Ketiso Yesu make mo maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ enisolomanu make iki paeyaonaęž‰ leke potopoto hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ witolo pitaęž‰ dupa alome. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke paęž‰taęž‰ homeke puki witaęž‰laęž‰ hau na pu make mandane tapake homeke na petolo pikitaęž‰ do ya peaęž‰peke alo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ peaęž‰peke.
\v 22 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ siosi paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaenaęž‰taęž‰ na hondomaęž‰ tiake hataęž‰ kiki witaęž‰laęž‰ hau aĚ±iĚ± na peaęž‰peke. Mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau neke paęž‰taęž‰ na mundilinaęž‰ leke nakaęž‰ hautaęž‰ yako pea hapeke.
\p 
\v 23 Neketaęž‰ yeni meaęž‰tiki pu haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ welekemaęž‰ epeke e pokenaęž‰ ikali homeke na neke waini siki make apaęž‰tao napeke.
\p 
\v 24 Mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ peneme peneme yao ulaęž‰me. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu piaęž‰peke nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumaęž‰taęž‰ iki hatuku ipilieke. Pate mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ wetepe nane peneme yaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ wilimikie.
\v 25 Mandane epeke haumanu make koto tupaęž‰ kone peneme peneme yao ulaęž‰me. Kutaataęž‰ mo otaęž‰ peneme na ulaęž‰ epeke hau mandane ekimanu maketaęž‰ aęž‰mbao wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\c 6
\s1 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 1 Mandane pa hameke e pokaaseme tapake ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ homu pea hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo pa haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki paęž‰taęž‰ make nikaęž‰ alomaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke pimanu na lelimikie.
\p 
\v 2 Mandane pa hameke e pokaaseme tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ you halitaęž‰ Ketiso hali hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke hone witolo hataęž‰ paa pa alemaęž‰ na handaapaęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki hone witolo Ipikitaęž‰ ya Ketiso kame halekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki hone paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokawaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ do e paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeke ale minaęž‰e hone wiaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ pokeme e tupaęž‰ na pokeketaęž‰ kotoeki lombei peao pokaapeke.
\s1 Makeaasaęž‰ hau walaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu
\p Do alo pi manutaęž‰ nate paeyao wopu saĚ±ęž‰tiaaso hataęž‰ walaęž‰tiki pu hapeke.
\v 3 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo hande nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi make mo nikaęž‰ hone tulao yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu make kotaęž‰ walomaęž‰ pi yaapo mandake na piki pa taęž‰taęž‰ piki manaęž‰ pimanu aęž‰pa waleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 4 kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ hone na wiki hakoko litaęž‰laęž‰ hali halaęž‰me. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone teke pilaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo manaęž‰ pi teke manunaęž‰taęž‰ ape ape lo make pi yokaalu alu puluekemaęž‰ hone wopu u halaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hone wopu epeke tupaęž‰ na handeteke haleme wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± IĚ± alaęž‰ hau make ape ape la alualu pitolo hataęž‰ yaalaęž‰ peake pi la alualu pu make na handomaęž‰ tiake hoke hone u alualu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make
\v 5 kimaęž‰ na homeke pi yokaalu alu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make kotaęž‰ hao paeyao mo wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰ tiao halaęž‰me. Kutu piki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande otaęž‰ pimanu minaęž‰paęž‰laaso hataęž‰taęž‰ pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hamoko hapeke potaęž‰e hone u halememe.
\p 
\v 6 Otaęž‰ alaęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ miniki halaęž‰ kenke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰e hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ hamoko some halaęž‰me.
\v 7 Nikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰taęž‰ aleke miniki epolomaęž‰pe. Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na miniki epolomaęž‰me. Pa do kenke minaęž‰paęž‰laomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aleke mea polumaęž‰pe. Diaęž‰me. Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mea polumeke.
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ ne akaęž‰manu anaęž‰naęž‰ wia haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ anaęž‰e.
\v 9 Mo hamoko haluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ne wiaasaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰pei leke hondalieke. Ikaęž‰ hone wopu na wiki hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ hoke hone manumaęž‰ iki yolaęž‰ mea lopao otaęž‰ hoeyaalieke.
\v 10 Mo mani we pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hoke haumanu pu tialo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teke ulaęž‰me. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mani muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu witolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulao halemeeki minaęž‰paęž‰lao hoke kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki tandamaęž‰ homo haememe.
\s1 Timodi paęž‰taęž‰ leeke manaęž‰ pimanu
\p 
\v 11 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hali hataęž‰taęž‰ koto hau manutaęž‰ mone hataęž‰ pinaęž‰ kiao papate leke hapeke. Kutu puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tikitiki piki hau make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau leke pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau make hone tulaasaęž‰ hau make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau make ki hone na wiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau make kimele piki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau make koto hau paeyao otaęž‰ muluekee hone u paleke pu hapeke.
\v 12 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hoto neli kitaęž‰laęž‰ nate ninaęž‰ mo hande tombo muluekemaęž‰ honkopu hao aĚ±iĚ±ya pu halememe. Koto tupaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo tombo wataasaęž‰ tupaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu hao aĚ±iĚ±ya pu hapeke. Koto deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasome alo hataęž‰ peneme yaeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ muelenaęž‰yeke neke wi leaęž‰me.
\v 13 Mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao daęž‰taa winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ make mo hande Pontiasi Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi leeke Ketiso Yesu ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ dupa alome.
\v 14 Mo peaęž‰pekee laa neke paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pi manunaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homa mo Tekehali Yesu Ketiso paa epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate epenaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeya hoeya na piki yopu miniki hao hapeke.
\v 15 Mo Ketisonaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la epolo paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke handeteke halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo ponkaęž‰ di pilu ulaęž‰ nate opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso peneme yao mea halieke. Kodaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teke hataęž‰ ipiki homeketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo kini haliweki paeyaonaęž‰ Tumiki Kini hali make mo teke haliweki paeyaonaęž‰ Tekehali make halaęž‰me.
\v 16 Ipiki homeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone pa daęž‰taa hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki halaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yeke paĚ±aĚ± tieke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na handemeke yeke Kodaęž‰ yeke handaataęž‰ ame make otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ biki tieke otaęž‰ kende winaęž‰ make mo na paeyeke pa hao halaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wele make ipikaęž‰eki winaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.
\s1 Hamoko wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 17 Mo kenke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ hamoko haseme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi la wiaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ hakoko na lu make mo aĚ±iĚ± paelo paęž‰laęž‰ kenke ale manunaęž‰ hone na ti lao hao hapaęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ niki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homomono epeke alemanu ku halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti lao hapaęž‰peke lapeke.
\v 18 Koto wandaęž‰hali ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau pipe laataęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hau piteme ekimaęž‰ hamoko hapaęž‰peke laa lapeke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke moke pitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hamoko ale manutaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pa teli pealuekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao hapaęž‰peke lapeke.
\v 19 Koto hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wetepe hapeke yolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ epeke teke u haenaęž‰ lelimikie. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki miniki hao halimikie.
\p 
\v 20 Timodio. Do Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ etaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu handeteke hapeke. Mo epe na piki Kodaęž‰ mataake pimanu la kiteme pi manutaęž‰ kiaapeke. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ makeaaso hataęž‰ Do alomaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ tumiki pie lo halememe.
\v 21 Kutupa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Koto aleme tumiki pitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me laa lemeke handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande otaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ haunaęž‰ potaęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laememe.
\p Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Timodi iki paęž‰taęž‰ hao haenaęž‰e. 
